---
title: Honey-Drizzled Paprika Chicken with Cheesy Garlic Butter Biscuits & Green Beans
description: It’s hard to beat the hands-off ease (and quick cleanup) of a sheet pan dinner. This version requires no chopping whatsoever—simply season chicken with paprika and garlic powder, then roast until juicy. Garlic butter biscuits bake on the same baking sheet with a melty Monterey Jack topping that’s truly next-level. We round out the plate with tender green beans, then drizzle the chicken with honey for sweet contrast to all that savory goodness. It’s all ready in just 30 minutes—now that’s a weeknight win!
